[node name="start_cutsccene" type="Node2D" unique_id=1750482943 groups=["cutscene", "main"]]
script = ExtResource("1_4rp7l")
dialoge = Array[String](["-Isn’t the world a huge place? In this vast world, there are so many fantastic things to see and countless heroic tales to read—dragons, dark lords, thieving goblins, blah blah.", "-And let’s go visit a hero who, for some reason, has found himself unemployed in this vast, troubled world. ", "-This knight is a brave hero who has been trained for a heroic role since childhood...", "-I mean, at least that's how it used to be. ", "-Strangely enough, this village was very peaceful. It had never been attacked or plundered. The villagers were very happy about this, but our knight felt that something was missing ", "-When the villagers’ taunts were added to this feeling, the knight could take no more ", "-and he turned to alcohol ", "-But one day, the danger that no one thought would ever come actually arrived ", "-A necromancer stormed the queen's castle with his soldiers.", "-When the knight heard the news, he was blind drunk, but there was nothing he could do. He wasn’t in any state to think straight anyway. ", "-He grabbed his sword, rushed out of the tavern, and started running toward the princess’s castle..."])

